'''Sith Hall''' was an exhibition hall within the [[Galactic Museum/Legends|Galactic Museum]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]], which was devoted to the history of the ancient [[Sith Empire/Legends|Sith Empire]]. By the time of [[Satal Keto/Legends|Satal]] and [[Aleema Keto]]'s arrival on Coruscant, the Hall was in the process of erecting a new exhibit, titled ''[[The Dark Lords of the Sith]]''. The display was incomplete, and the Ketos managed to steal a [[Sith spellbook/Legends|Sith spellbook]] from the Hall when the Museum curator was preoccupied with a [[Comlink/Legends|comlink]].

